{"tid":898993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌忍撚夠你條蝻亞狗","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T06:14:13.000Z","uid":201749,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16c2abbdcdfbc44c7fa585a8ebcb0f93ee5e7a63","tid":898993,"uid":201749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的,大專英文科pj自由分組,隔幾堂就交份group assignment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實workload認真唔算大,都係寫幾隻字就夠屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬第一堂就叫我地分四五個人一組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,唸住是鳩但啦做幾份功課,同邊個一組都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就同坐前面聽嗰兩條蝻啞狗一組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點撚知原來佢地係弱撚智小兒麻痺陽痿向左走向右走咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作幾段字成半個月後交,第二日就做撚完send上group問我佢寫成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢上堂都柒下柒下咁,篇文好得去邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇都廢時<br />\n<br />\n點知呢個禮拜佢係撚咁send問號洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 追數都冇你咁煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經忍唔撚到落去,有冇人教我印度粗口一句車鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e53aa273bfbaac7faf12d2fb4c32e4cd2af07d","tid":898993,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"你叫佢用左手食飯咪得<br />\n<br />\nUse left hand eat rice ok?"},{"pid":"e90825ad04216095c7fb534fdbb63d0c3d7e80e7","tid":898993,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"bobo"},{"pid":"174d31c84b8a273ea862079cf02a4e2e1fb2637d","tid":898993,"uid":24576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=